[49m[38;5;10m+    210[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    211[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## General Architecture Pattern
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    212[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    213[0m:[38;5;10m[49m A healthcare care coordination assistant decomposes into ten logical stages: journey enrollment with care-plan ingestion and milestone decomposition, longitudinal-store initialization with multi-system context aggregation, channel entry with disclosure refresh, input safety screening with continuous emergency screening, identity-and-context loading across systems, conversation handling with milestone-aware grounded responses, output safety screening with scope verification, action proposal with deterministic execution, escalation routing to human coordinators when applicable, and audit logging with cross-system event correlation. The cross-cutting concerns from recipes 11.1 through 11.8 carry forward; this recipe adds five new ones (multi-system orchestration as architectural primitive, milestone-tracking pipeline with explicit state machines, records-flow workflow as first-class component, family-and-caregiver consent posture, and cross-institutional information-flow integration).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    214[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    215[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    216[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── JOURNEY ENROLLMENT + CARE-PLAN INGESTION ──────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    217[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    218[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Triggered by clinical event]                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    219[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Discharge from hospital                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    220[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Specialist diagnosis with multi-provider workup      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    221[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pregnancy enrollment in prenatal care                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    222[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-procedure care plan                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    223[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Care-management program enrollment                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    224[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient self-enrollment per institutional policy     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    225[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    226[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    227[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Care-plan ingestion]                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    228[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull signed care plan from EHR (FHIR CarePlan)       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    229[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Decompose into milestones with windows, dependencies,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    230[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      and escalation criteria                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    231[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Each milestone has explicit state machine and        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    232[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      completion semantics                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    233[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Validate against journey-template (cardiac discharge,│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    234[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      oncology, maternity, complex pediatrics)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    235[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull patient demographic and consent context         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    236[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull family-caregiver context (where designated)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    237[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull recent encounter history                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    238[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull active medications                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    239[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull insurance and benefits context                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    240[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pull social-determinants context (where collected)   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    241[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    242[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    243[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: instantiated journey with milestones,          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    244[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    longitudinal store ready, engagement schedule prepared]│
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    245[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    246[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    247[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    248[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── LONGITUDINAL STORE INITIALIZATION ─────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    249[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    250[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-coordinator longitudinal store]                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    251[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active journeys (one or more concurrent)             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    252[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active milestones across journeys                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    253[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-provider context (PCP, specialists, ancillary) │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    254[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent encounter history (institutional and HIE)     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    255[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active referrals with state                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    256[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active records-release requests with state           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    257[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Active appointments (scheduled, completed, no-show)  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    258[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pharmacy fill history                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    259[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation history (initially empty)               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    260[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Stated patient and caregiver preferences             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    261[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent state (general, caregiver, HIE, 42 CFR)      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    262[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Social-determinants flags                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    263[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Mental-health-comorbidity flags                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    264[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    265[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Storage architecture]                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Structured data: DynamoDB tables with care-          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      coordination-specific encryption keys                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Conversation transcript: S3 with vector retrieval    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Multi-system event log: time-ordered events from     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      EHR, referral, scheduling, records-release, pharmacy │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    271[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Recent-context summary: cached, refreshed per        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    272[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      conversation                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    273[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    274[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    275[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: longitudinal store ready for coordination      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    276[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    conversations]                                         │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    277[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    278[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    279[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    280[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── CHANNEL ENTRY WITH DISCLOSURE REFRESH ─────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    281[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    282[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Patient-initiated entry]                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    283[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - In-app chat (most common)                            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    284[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - SMS (with consent)                                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    285[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Web chat                                             │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    286[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Voice channel (where supported)                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    287[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    288[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Caregiver-initiated entry, where consented]            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    289[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Designated proxy access                              │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    290[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Consent-state checked before any patient context     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    291[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      is exposed                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    292[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    293[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Bot-initiated entry, scheduled or event-driven]        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    294[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Pre-appointment nudge                                │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    295[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Post-appointment follow-up                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    296[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Milestone-window nudge                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    297[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Records-flow gap notification                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    298[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Missed-appointment re-engagement                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    299[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Coordination-degradation surfacing                   │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    300[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    301[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Disclosure refresh per session or defined cadence]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    302[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I'm a chat tool, not a person"                      │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    303[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "I help with coordinating your care; I don't make    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    304[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      clinical decisions"                                  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    305[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - "If you're having an emergency, call 911"            │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    306[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Patient acknowledges or continues                    │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    307[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           │                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    308[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │           ▼                                               │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    309[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Output: session_id, channel, auth context, disclosure  │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    310[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    acknowledged]                                          │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    311[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    312[0m:[38;5;10m[49m └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    313[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    314[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ┌────────── INPUT SAFETY + EMERGENCY SCREEN ───────────────┐
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    315[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    316[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Standard input safety primitives from recipe 11.1]     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    317[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Prompt-injection detection                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    318[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - PHI minimization                                     │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    319[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Scope-attempt detection (diagnosis, medication       │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    320[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │      adjustment, therapy)                                 │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    321[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │                                                           │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    322[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │   [Continuous emergency screening]                        │
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    323[0m:[38;5;10m[49m │    - Acute symptom presentations (chest pain, severe      │
